original_title: HOW TO GET DRY ICE IN MASSACHUSETTS
overview: Dry ice ain’t easy to come by these days. Especially in Massachusetts. But you probably had no idea, right? You think this doesn’t affect you? Think again. The shortage actually says a lot about society. Try being less ignorant next time.  You’ll be alright though, here’s a tutorial(s).
